  "chapters": [
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch1",
      "text": "The city lights are dazzling tonight. Didn’t expect to run into you here, Bob.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch2",
      "text": "Fate works in mysterious ways, Alex. Or maybe you were looking for me?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch3",
      "text": "Oh, confident, are we? Maybe I was. Or maybe it’s just coincidence.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch4",
      "text": "Either way, you’re here. And I have a feeling this night is about to get interesting.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch5",
      "text": "You always had a way with words, Bob. Where were you headed before this chance encounter?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch6",
      "text": "Honestly? Nowhere special. But now, I think I found my destination.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch7",
      "text": "Smooth. But if you’re staying, you owe me a drink.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch8",
      "text": "Only if you promise to tell me something interesting in return.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch9",
      "text": "Deal. But I get to choose what’s interesting.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch10",
      "text": "Fair enough. Let’s grab that drink and see where the night takes us.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch11",
      "text": "The bar’s packed, but I think I see a free table in the corner.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch12",
      "text": "Lead the way. I’ll get the drinks. What’s your poison?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch13",
      "text": "Surprise me. But nothing too sweet—I’m not that easy to figure out.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch14",
      "text": "Noted. A drink as mysterious as you coming right up.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch15",
      "text": "Let’s see if you live up to the challenge.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch16",
      "text": "A drink, a challenge, and good company? This might be my kind of night.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch17",
      "text": "Don’t get ahead of yourself. We’ll see how the night goes.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch18",
      "text": "I like a challenge, Alex. Keeps things interesting.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch19",
      "text": "Then you’re in luck. I don’t make things easy.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch20",
      "text": "Now I’m really intrigued.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch21",
      "text": "So, tell me something interesting. I’m curious what you have in mind.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch22",
      "text": "Something interesting? I’ll tell you about a place I’ve always wanted to visit. Maybe you’ll join me one day.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch23",
      "text": "That sounds intriguing. Where is this mysterious place?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch24",
      "text": "It’s a secret for now. But maybe, if the night goes well, I’ll let you in on it.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch25",
      "text": "I’m looking forward to finding out more, Bob. Let’s see where the night takes us.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    }
